{"tid":1605621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爭取外國勢力支持要不分黨派  幾時先學得識？","createTime":"2019-09-30T10:41:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T08:56:21.000Z","uid":89160,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"be22c3c926676b8fd14ac8e4e8ca8f68e76e7148","tid":1605621,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:41:32.000Z","msg":"講左好多次，人地內政唔關你事，你撐侵好，撐美國民主黨又好，<strong><ins>唔該大家將你既支持同人地既政治派別掛勾</ins></strong>，好似我之前出 post 話民主黨眾議員Rick Larsen唔支持《民主法》，就個個係到話「美國民主黨都係賣香港」，唔好咁小學雞好冇？條 Act 大把 democrats co-sponsor 啦。<br />\n<br />\n又好似 Hong Kong Hermit  批評共和黨參議員 Rick Scott 既政見，呢d係佢作為其中一個美國人既意見，尊重就得架啦，唔駛跟架！人地內部政治，關你撚事咩！Rick Scott 唔係票咩？<br />\n<br />\n人地黎到香港視察咪支持囉，最緊要唔好懶醒牽涉佢既本土政見。美國人醫療政策，同投票駛唔駛身份證關香港撚事咩？我都認為投票要身份證，但唔該你喺人地面前就咪多口啦！<br />\n<br />\n求求大家，唔好將你對美國政壇既意見同香港事務掛勾，我地係希望全光譜既支持，尤其美國本身就好 divided ，如果我地玩錯一步就煩架啦！<br />\n<br />\n唔該！"},{"pid":"f65daf731479629bd1cd96e2eba1c06d7edde599","tid":1605621,"uid":89160,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:45:51.000Z","msg":"民間外交好重要唔可以亂玩架"},{"pid":"b6b4aa24b13345b4b43977df252fbb7962ade753","tid":1605621,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263e43ad95ddba9182b34525892872175d641426","tid":1605621,"uid":30697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:53:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"614d9b61df2e99291ecff749c7900bd7f013080f","tid":1605621,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1eb30f8938ce52b239894367bb74169b0846bc","tid":1605621,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.fub